-# Offcanvas help drawer for problems/edit.
-# Triggered by the Help (?) icon button in the edit-page header.
-# Content here is intended to grow over time; keep sections short and
-# link out to the wiki for deep reference rather than duplicating it.
#problem-edit-help.offcanvas.offcanvas-end.offcanvas-help{tabindex: -1, 'aria-labelledby': 'problem-edit-help-label'}
  .offcanvas-header.border-bottom
    %div
      %h5#problem-edit-help-label.offcanvas-title.fw-bold.mb-0
        %span.mi.me-1 help_outline
        Problem Editor Help
      %small.text-secondary Quick reference for the fields and panels on this page.
    %button.btn-close{type: 'button', 'data-bs-dismiss': 'offcanvas', 'aria-label': 'Close'}

  .offcanvas-body
    -# ---- Section: Detail fields ----
    %section.mb-4
      %h6.fw-bold.text-secondary.text-uppercase.small.ls-1.mb-2 Detail Card
      %dl.row.small.mb-0
        %dt.col-4.fw-semibold Full name
        %dd.col-8.text-secondary Human-readable title shown to students. Required.
        %dt.col-4.fw-semibold Name
        %dd.col-8.text-secondary
          Short identifier used in filenames and the engine. Must be
          %strong unique
          and stable — renaming may break links and imports.
        %dt.col-4.fw-semibold Description
        %dd.col-8.text-secondary Markdown statement shown to students.
        %dt.col-4.fw-semibold Time / memory limit
        %dd.col-8.text-secondary Per-test-case caps. Time in seconds, memory in MB.
        %dt.col-4.fw-semibold Tags
        %dd.col-8.text-secondary
          Free-form labels. For viva exams, attach
          %code llm_prompt
          (interviewer persona + rubric) and
          %code viva_grounding
          (course materials) here.

    -# ---- Section: Datasets ----
    %section.mb-4
      %h6.fw-bold.text-secondary.text-uppercase.small.ls-1.mb-2 Datasets
      %p.small.text-secondary.mb-2
        A problem can have multiple datasets; exactly one is the
        %strong live dataset
        — that's what runs when a student submits. Switch the live
        dataset via the dropdown on the right.
      %p.small.text-secondary.mb-0
        Viva-exam problems don't use datasets at all — they're driven by
        the LLM tags described above.

    -# ---- Section: Audit & ops ----
    %section.mb-4
      %h6.fw-bold.text-secondary.text-uppercase.small.ls-1.mb-2 Operations
      %ul.small.text-secondary.mb-0.ps-3
        %li
          %span.mi.md-18.align-text-bottom query_stats
          %strong Statistics
          — submission counts, scores, language breakdown.
        %li
          %span.mi.md-18.align-text-bottom download
          %strong Download Archive
          — exports the problem + live dataset for backup or transfer.
        %li
          %span.mi.md-18.align-text-bottom history
          %strong Change history
          — audit log of edits to this problem, its dataset, and testcases.

    -# ---- Section: External links ----
    %section
      %h6.fw-bold.text-secondary.text-uppercase.small.ls-1.mb-2 More
      %p.small.text-secondary.mb-1
        For deep reference (import format, checker scripts, manager files,
        initializer scripts) see the project wiki.
      -# TODO: replace with the actual wiki URL once we pick one
      %a.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-secondary.d-inline-flex.align-items-center.gap-1{href: '#', target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener'}
        %span.mi.md-18 open_in_new
        Open wiki
